### PyTkPlot - a Python 3 Class to plot graphs inside  a tkinter canvas


### Authors and Contributors
It is a small project started as an exercise. If you want to contribute, let me know!

### Support or Contact
[Please report any bugs on the tracker.](https://github.com/mauriciodev/pytkplot/issues)
